# FILE: .../studentDashboard/marketplaceLedger/serviceContracts.desc
# ROLE: Freelance Project & Escrow Management Terminal
# VIBE: Professional / High-Trust / Milestone-Driven / 90-Degree Precision

## 1. THE "ESCROW LOCK" STATUS (Top Fold)
- **VISUAL:** A prominent, high-contrast box showing "Funds in Security."
- **LOGIC:** Displays the total amount of ShamCash currently held by the Platform (AMJ) for active jobs.
- **DATA:** [ 🔒 Total Escrow: 1,200,000 SYP ] | [ 💼 Active Contracts: 3 ].
- **MANTRA:** "Your money is safe until the work is delivered. Challenge Every Day."

## 2. THE ACTIVE CONTRACTS BOARD (The Project List)
- **FORMAT:** A vertical stack of "Service Cards" with a linear timeline.
- **CARD COMPONENTS:**
    - **FREELANCER:** Avatar + Name (e.g., "Samer - Full Stack Developer").
    - **PROJECT TITLE:** "Faculty Website - Backend Refactor."
    - **STATUS PILLS:** - [ 🕒 Awaiting Payment ] - Receipt uploaded, waiting for Admin.
        - [ ⚙️ In Progress ] - Work is being done.
        - [ 📦 Under Review ] - Freelancer submitted the files.
        - [ ✅ Completed ] - Funds released.
- **DEADLINE:** "Due in: 3 Days" (Counts down in Red if overdue).

## 3. THE "MILESTONE & DELIVERY" DRAWER
- **LOGIC:** Clicking a contract expands a detailed view.
- **FILES ZONE:** Direct links to Google Drive folders where the freelancer has uploaded the work.
- **APPROVAL ACTION:** A high-alert button: **[ 🔓 Release Payment ]**.
    - **WARNING MODAL:** "By clicking this, you confirm the work is finished and the money will be sent to the Freelancer. This cannot be undone."

## 4. THE BID & OFFER QUEUE (Incoming Proposals)
- **VISUAL:** A secondary list for "Custom Requests" the student has posted.
- **DATA:** - **Offer:** "I can solve this logic set for 50k SYP."
    - **Freelancer Rank:** [ 🌟 Elite ].
- **ACTION:** [ ✅ Accept Offer ] - Generates a new Contract and prompts for ShamCash payment.

## 5. DISPUTE & COMMUNICATION HUB
- **MESSAGING:** A "Direct to Telegram/WhatsApp" button for the specific freelancer assigned to the project.
- **DISPUTE BUTTON:** [ ⚠️ Report Issue ] - Alerts the Admin (AMJ) to freeze the Escrow and mediate the conflict if the quality is poor.

## 6. STICKY ACTION HUD
- **POST NEW JOB:** [ ➕ Request a Custom Service ] -> Redirects to the Service Catalog.
- **HISTORY:** [ 📜 View Finished Contracts ] - Archives of all successfully completed projects.